cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CY 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of "cs.CL" (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing tasks such as grammatical error correction. The use of neural networks also suggests that it could belong to "cs.LG" (Machine Learning) and "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence). The focus on developing a new model also suggests that it could belong to "cs.NE" (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the mention of character-level information suggests that it could belong to "cs.CY" (Computational Geometry).
